\{ essay_box(4,60) \}
$PAR
(b) For the representative slice of thickness \(\triangle x\) that is located horizontally at a location \(x\) (somewhere between \(x = 0\) and \(x = 5\)), what is the radius of the representative slice?  Note that the radius depends on the value of \(x\). $BR 
\{ essay_box(4,60) \}
$PAR
